info.author: kakkoii1337
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.name: gai-lib-gen
info.summary: Gai/Gen is the Universal Multi-Modal Wrapper Library for LLM. The library is designed to provide a simplified and unified interface for seamless switching between multi-modal open source language models on a local machine and OpenAI APIs.
